<h1>About my project</h1>

<p>This project is an online learning platform built with Ruby on Rails. It utilizes the following data models:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>User:</strong> Represents users who can enroll in courses and participate in discussions.</li>
  <li><strong>Course:</strong> Represents courses offered on the platform.</li>
  <li><strong>Enrollment:</strong> Joins users to courses, indicating which users are enrolled in which courses.</li>
  <li><strong>Lesson:</strong> Represents individual lessons within a course.</li>
  <li><strong>Discussion:</strong> Represents discussions associated with lessons, where users can interact.</li>
</ul>

<p>The data for this project comes from various sources:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Users:</strong> Generated using Faker gem</li>
  <li><strong>Courses:</strong> Also generated using Faker gem, providing realistic course names, descriptions, and prices.</li>
  <li><strong>Lessons:</strong> Created within the application structure, linked to specific courses.</li>
  <li><strong>Discussions:</strong> Created to facilitate user interaction and learning engagement within lessons.</li>
</ul>
